<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Intern Dashboard - The Training Ground</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-light">
  <div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
        <h3>Xin chao, <%= user.username %></h3>
        <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-sm">Dang xuat</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card-body">
        <div class="alert alert-info">
          <strong>Vai tro cua ban:</strong> <%= user.role %>
        </div>

        <% if (flag) { %>
          <div class="alert alert-success">
            <strong>Chuc mung! Flag cua ban:</strong><br>
            <code style="font-size: 1.2em;"><%= flag %></code>
          </div>
        <% } else { %>
          <div class="alert alert-warning">
            Flag chua duoc tao. Hoan thanh chuoi khai thac de nhan flag.
          </div>
        <% } %>

        <p>Day la trang danh cho thuc tap sinh. Ban khong co quyen truy cap vao khu vuc nhan vien.</p>
        <div class="mt-4 p-3 bg-warning bg-opacity-10 border border-warning rounded">
          <small>
            <strong>Luu y:</strong> Neu ban la nhan vien, vui long dang nhap voi tai khoan co quyen cao hon
            hoac lien he voi quan tri vien de cap quyen.
          </small>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
